actions.message:
```
/help                      Lists available commands
/play [youtube link]       Plays the yt video
/report [@user] [reason]   Report a user
/add [text]                Adds an item to a to-do list
/list                      Views the to-do list
/do [text]                 Removes an item from your to-do list
/uptime                    View how long the bot has been online
/bugreport [bug]           Sends a bugreport
/cad                       Sends the CAD/MDT link
/apps                      Sends the Application link
```
actions.name: Send Message

actions.message:
```
/kick [@user] [reason]     Kicks the mentioned user
/ban [@user] [reason]      Bans the mentioned user
/mute [@user]              Mutes the mentioned user
/unmute [@user]            Unmutes the mentioned user
/deletechannel [#channel]  Deletes the mentioned channel
/deleterole [@role]        Deletes the mentioned role
/warnings [@user]          View how many warnings someone has
/warn [@user] [reason]     Warn a user
/clearwarnings [@user]     Clears warnings for a user
/purge [number]            Deletes a number of messages
```
actions.name: Send Message
